      "span_text": "The designers can make more informed behavior designs when they have a better understanding of the information the agent has available. [CITATION_1] For example, in Figure 4 the darker player near the top of the window perceives that he is in an empty space on the eld although it is not, as can be seen from the RoboCup Soccermonitor (see Figure 5 ).",
